&lt;p&gt;Installing &amp;ldquo;Guest Tools&amp;rdquo; significantly enhances the user experience with VMware virtual machines (VMs). As of September 2015, VMware recommends using the distribution-specific open-vm-tools (OVT) instead of the VMware Tools package for guest machines.&lt;/p&gt;
